                      "id": "byidW",
                      "name": "card2sub",
                      "fill": "#FF3B30",
                      "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                      "width": "fill_container",
                      "content": "Meeting intelligence product with searchable transcripts and team summaries.",
                      "lineHeight": 1.5,
                      "fontFamily": "Inter",
                      "fontSize": 12,
                      "fontWeight": "normal"
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "id": "lFYQL",
                      "name": "card2body",
                      "fill": "#D0D0D0",
                      "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                      "width": "fill_container",
                      "content": "OVERVIEW\nAutomated speech-to-text plus searchable knowledge capture.\n\nCORE PRODUCT\nRecording, transcription, summaries, team search.\n\nPOSITIONING\nBroad productivity and meeting memory.\n\nSTRENGTHS\nTeam utility, searchable archive.\n\nLIMITATIONS\nLess creator-specific than editing-led tools.\n\nPRICING MODEL\nFree + per-user plans.\n\nTARGET AUDIENCE\nMeeting-heavy teams, operators, knowledge workers.",
                      "lineHeight": 1.55,
                      "fontFamily": "IBM Plex Mono",
                      "fontSize": 10,
                      "fontWeight": "500"
                    }
                  ]
