                      "content": "OVERVIEW\nProduction platform for recording, editing, and publishing.\n\nCORE PRODUCT\nRecording, editing, hosting-adjacent creation tools.\n\nPOSITIONING\nSimplified production for creators.\n\nSTRENGTHS\nEnd-to-end narrative, streamlined flow.\n\nLIMITATIONS\nMay be narrower outside podcast production.\n\nPRICING MODEL\nSubscription plans.\n\nTARGET AUDIENCE\nPodcast creators and small media teams.",
