                      "children": [
                        {
                          "type": "text",
                          "id": "OfotB",
                          "name": "mktGenTitle",
                          "fill": "#0A0A0A",
                          "content": "Marketing Plan — PodPacer",
                          "fontFamily": "Space Grotesk",
                          "fontSize": 30,
                          "fontWeight": "700"
                        },
                        {
                          "type": "text",
                          "id": "yXMAl",
                          "name": "mktGenBody1",
                          "fill": "#444444",
                          "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                          "width": "fill_container",
                          "content": "## Brief Inputs\nTarget audience: PMs at SaaS startups\nStage: MVP\nBudget: $2k / month\nLaunch window: next 2 weeks\nChannels: Product Hunt, X, HN, Reddit, email\n\n## Positioning\nPodPacer helps busy listeners reclaim time with semantic skipping and creator-aware playback controls.",
                          "lineHeight": 1.7,
                          "fontFamily": "Inter",
                          "fontSize": 13,
                          "fontWeight": "normal"
                        },
                        {
                          "type": "text",
                          "id": "ovWsz",
                          "name": "mktGenBody2",
                          "fill": "#444444",
                          "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                          "width": "fill_container",
                          "content": "## Channel Priority\n1. Product Hunt\n2. X\n3. Founder communities\n\n## Budget Allocation\n- Content and creative: 40%\n- Distribution and boosts: 40%\n- Experiments: 20%\n\n## Copy Pack (MVP)\nOne-liner: PodPacer helps PMs at SaaS startups move from noisy listening to faster signal capture.\n\n## 14-Day Execution Checklist\n- Finalize positioning\n- Prepare launch assets\n- Ship first 3 posts\n- Track signups and activation",
                          "lineHeight": 1.7,
                          "fontFamily": "Inter",
                          "fontSize": 13,
                          "fontWeight": "normal"
                        }
                      ]
                    }
                  ]
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    }
